Actelis Networks, Inc. engages in the design, development, manufacture, and marketing of cyber hardened, hybrid fiber, copper networking solutions for Internet of Things and telecommunication companies in North America, Europe, the Middle East, Africa, Latin America, and the Asia Pacific. It provides cyber-hardened, rapid-deployment networking solutions for wide-area IoT applications, including federal, state, and local governments; intelligent traffic systems; and military, utility, rail, telecom, and campus applications. The company's products include ethernet access switches; network aggregator switches; industrial managed ethernet switches and extenders; ethernet first mile repeaters; broadband amplifiers; and Advanced MetaLIGHT element management systems software, which enables remote management, monitoring, maintenance, and configuration of the installed equipment in the network. It serves offers its products through system integrators, distributors, contractors, resellers, and consultants. The company was incorporated in 1998 and is headquartered in Fremont, California.